				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Chu-trung-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-Nguy%C3%AAn-C%E1%BB%ADu-thi/poem-O6CufLa0BHsoVVsbTerwbA">Chu trung độc Nguyên Cửu thi - 舟中讀元九詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/D%E1%BA%A1-tranh/poem-zNq9uR8QBeyPgfW3Nl_KUw">Dạ tranh - 夜箏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/D%C4%A9-k%C3%ADnh-t%E1%BA%B7ng-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-HbgK3vKm_kodDFAsVgQ2Xw">Dĩ kính tặng biệt - 以鏡贈別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4n/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-C%E1%BB%A9u-s%C6%A1n/poem-aCoEvYmg2S8s7KzdgfH5aQ">Đông Cứu sơn - 東究山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4n/author-YDc3orDW4enWycHMfed3Ww">Lê Quý Đôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%99-xu%C3%A2n/poem-o2duPTYx6mbDB3Hq_PWWOg">Mộ xuân - 暮春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-Nghi%C3%AAm-trung-th%E1%BB%ABa-T%C3%A2y-th%C3%A0nh-v%C3%A3n-di%E1%BB%83u-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem--PN92De3PhqGYRhxd0JEvA">Phụng hoạ Nghiêm trung thừa “Tây thành vãn diểu” thập vận - 奉和嚴中丞西城晚眺十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Thu-ph%E1%BB%91-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-17/poem-vsq8Tn3bQkvLvV-qh8MAlA">Thu phố ca kỳ 17 - 秋浦歌其十七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%89nh-%C4%91%E1%BB%83-d%E1%BA%ABn-ng%C3%A2n-b%C3%ACnh/poem-fEvivJabPd3uwuqTNX3otg">Tỉnh để dẫn ngân bình - 井底引銀瓶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%E1%BA%BF-L%C3%A2n/Tr%C6%B0-%C4%91i%E1%BB%83u-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-1XdbBzJbNi0cFA9_xS9Eiw">Trư điểu đề - 猪鳥啼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%E1%BA%BF-L%C3%A2n/author-ZqTE_3GO97Ws9hNrgzlGIw">Ngô Thế Lân</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
